Description:
Specify the VT skew configuration required

Usage: set_vt_skew_config [-help]
                          [-analysis_mode {setup hold both}] [-clocks_only]
                          [-correlated_vt_groups <corr_group>]
                          [-exclude <exclude>] [-exclude_nominal]
                          [-include_only <include_only>]
                          [-unique_vt_mode {none slow fast nominal}]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-analysis_mode {setup hold both}       # Analysis mode for which the
                                       # configuration is to be used
                                       # (enum, optional)
-clocks_only                           # Only consider launch and capture clock
                                       # VTs post CPPR point when enumerating
                                       # (bool, optional)
-correlated_vt_groups <corr_group>     # specify groups for correlation
                                       # (string, optional)
-exclude <exclude>                     # specify config to be excluded
                                       # (string, optional)
-exclude_nominal                       # only enumerate fast/slow combinations
                                       # (bool, optional)
-include_only <include_only>           # specify config to be only included
                                       # (string, optional)
-unique_vt_mode {none slow fast nominal}
                                       # VT mode to be used as dominant (enum, optional)